Uses of Package
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client

Packages that use com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client Defines the Rhizosphere visualization widget and all the main interfaces required to configure and instantiate a Rhizosphere visualization within GWT. 
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.bootstrap Internal support classes to prepare and deploy Rhizosphere visualizations. 
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.gviz Classes to expose Rhizosphere as a standard visualization compatible with the Google Visualization APIs for GWT. 
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.handlers Handlers and event definitions for events triggered by Rhizosphere visualizations. 
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.meta Classes to handle Rhizosphere metamodel configuration and generation. 
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.renderer Classes and interfaces for the generation and management of Rhizosphere renderings, that is, visual representation of Rhizosphere models. 
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.rebind Definition of Rhizosphere generators that convert POJOs (externally provided by users of this GWT module) into model objects suitable for use by the Rhizosphere underlying javascript library. 
 

Classes in com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client used by com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client

          Widget wrapping a Rhizosphere visualization.

          Callback interface to collect the outcome of programmatic requests sent to a Rhizosphere visualization.

          Callback interface equivalent to RhizosphereCallback that accepts an extra typed parameter as notification payload.

          Enumeration of the datatypes ('kinds' in Rhizosphere terminology) that can be assigned to Rhizosphere model attributes.
RhizosphereLazyPanel.RhizosphereBuilder
          Builder interface the RhizosphereLazyPanel delegates the actual Rhizosphere visualization building to.
RhizosphereLoader
          Loader to inject Rhizosphere javascript libraries into a GWT host page.
RhizosphereMapping
          Maps functionalities between externally defined POJOs and the object model Rhizosphere requires to operate.
RhizosphereMetaModel
          Enumerates and characterizes the attributes of Rhizosphere visualization models.
RhizosphereMetaModel.Attribute
          A single metamodel attribute.
RhizosphereMetaModel.DateClusterCriteria
          Enumeration of valid clustering criteria for Attribute#setDateClusterBy(DateClusterCriteria) settings.
RhizosphereModel
          Marker interface that identifies POJOs to use as Rhizopshere visualization models.
RhizosphereModelPosition
          Simple wrapper to declare an explicit positioning of a Rhizosphere model within the visualization viewport.
RhizosphereModelRef
          An opaque pointer holding a reference to a Rhizosphere model.
RhizosphereOptions
          Rhizosphere configuration options.
RhizosphereOptions.LayoutConstraints
          A map of constraints for the area that Rhizosphere will use to lay out models' renderings.
RhizosphereOptions.LogLevel
          Enumeration of logging levels that the Rhizosphere visualization can use for client-side logging.
RhizosphereOptions.PanningMode
          Enumeration of the panning modes that the Rhizosphere visualization allows for scrolling and panning gestures.
RhizosphereOptions.ResizeTrackingMode
          Enumeration of the resize tracking modes that the Rhizosphere visualization supports.
RhizosphereOptions.SelectionMode
          Enumeration of selection modes that the Rhizosphere visualization allows.
RhizosphereRenderer
          A renderer provides a visual representation of visualization models.
RhizosphereSelectionManager
          The Selection Manager keeps track of which models within a Rhizosphere visualization are currently selected, deselected, hidden or focused upon.
